__site_tagline1__: ZX Spectrum is a great retro platform and a welcoming community. But how do you start developing software for ZX Spectrum without spending months learning the stuff?
__site_tagline2__: We've made this site for those with a fondness for pixel graphics and 8-bit music who have decided to break into our creative world.
__site_tagline3__: Here we collect the most up-to-date developer background information and platform news and translate it into Russian, English and Spanish to make it as accessible as possible for everyone.
